ident?"},{"pid":"bd4506df575a646c1ea54dbdd95084d8bc33ef78","tid":1696861,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T15:13:47.000Z","msg":"The principal is the chief executive and the chief academic officer of a university or college <br />\n<br />\n其實幾種用法都ok...."},{"pid":"5e49800f016df5b26778148541032499cf7ac99d","tid":1696861,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f53ac4b7fd0e4963452576594a0249cc018fb508","tid":1696861,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T15:11:58.000Z","msg":"其實通唔通用？ 我都明 老師叫teacher 但係大學叫professor <br />\n但佢又真係校長喎 定係大學校高級d叫president?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T15:14:51.000Z","msg":"Professor (commonly abbreviated as prof.) is an academic rank at most universities and colleges. The word professor comes from Latin. It means a &quot;person who professes&quot;, being usually an expert in arts or sciences. A professor is a teacher of the highest rank<br />\n<br />\n呢個就通常無人調轉用"},{"pid":"0246a539092f850a751cdaec37439d0a936daa0e","tid":1696861,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T15:24:14.000Z","msg":"間間U唔同體制<br />\n香港用President主要係Chancellor(校監)由港督做而Vice-Chancellor先係校長<br />\n<br />\n頭2大跟足Vice-Chancellor and President呢個標準名義<br />\nVice-Chancellor擺前，因為Vice-Chancellor先係校長<br />\n<br />\nPresident點黎呢? 反而係取行政首長意思<br />\n<br />\n間間U校長都唔同名義<br />\n只係剛好香港全部當中都包含President呢隻字"},{"pid":"4c02b0da561878c44ce76d8032966b365e041917","tid":1696861,"uid":81167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T15:25:02.000Z","msg":"president 最簡單易讀"},{"pid":"e8e624b7146b5f3c6494c85e52ad47438bf7ac2f","tid":1696861,"uid":57237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f53ac4b7fd0e4963452576594a0249cc018fb508","tid":1696861,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T15:11:58.000Z","msg":"其實通唔通用？ 我都明 老師叫teacher 但係大學叫professor <br />\n但佢又真係校長喎 定係大學校高級d叫president?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T15:26:26.000Z","msg":"Professor 係教授啊"},{"pid":"d5911eb4724e10fa0cbe8722bc9ae611a060b80b","tid":1696861,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T15:27:14.000Z","msg":"係Vice Chancellor <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d28b5d9e01fe6cd58b2656cdd4fa78937195be","tid":1696861,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T15:38:44.000Z","msg":"全部叫阿sir算啦"},{"pid":"cc3b7002aba890d278970de34811e76c71ed7508","tid":1696861,"uid":153,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T15:40:08.000Z","msg":"叫開廢柴 縮頭烏龜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ff8b48f31f61f490c4871da5c8c7b9a52572a3f","tid":1696861,"uid":73611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5911eb4724e10fa0cbe8722bc9ae611a060b80b","tid":1696861,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T15:27:14.000Z","msg":"係Vice Chancellor <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T15:52:43.000Z","msg":"科大唔係咁叫喎"},{"pid":"3b8d7483f2d224113a1d1ac2c7a0a867535e6497","tid":1696861,"uid":276110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T15:55:34.000Z","msg":"原本港大同中大喺97前，都係依照英國傳統，叫校長做Vice Chancellor，原因上面有巴打講咗。但97後，當權者開始從各方面「去英國化」，但係班當權者不學無術，識啲唔識啲，以為用美式英文或者美式做法，就等於去英國化。於是，企得唔夠硬、歷史唔夠長嘅大學，咪跟住改叫President囉。港大呢啲想企硬，但又驚得罪當權者，於是整咗個不倫不類嘅title : &quot;President and Vice Chancellor&quot;.<br />\n<br />\nBy the way, 大家有冇留意，97前政府嘅電視英文廣告（或者博物館啲英語解說），全部都係英國口音，但而家睇到嘅政府英文廣告，已經聽唔到英國口音，基本上係北美或類北美口音！"}]}